casebody.data:
Timothy WHITE, et al., petitioners,
v.
REGENTS OF the UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA, et al. No. 15-667. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 25, 2016.

Motion of The American Association of Physical Anthropologists, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of The Ohio Archaeological Council, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
